      <li><strong>Local manufacturers in Punjab and Delhi:</strong> Ludhiana, Jalandhar, and Delhi's Wazirpur Industrial Area have dozens of tandoor fabricators who build custom gas tandoors at competitive prices. Quality varies — always inspect before purchase or buy through verified platforms.</li>
    </ul>

